 * bb  is the resolution in number of bits (8, 10, 12)
 * c   is the number of channels (1, 2, 4, 8)
 * sss is the maximum conversion speed (021 for 200 kSPS, 051 for 500
 kSPS and 101 for 1 MSPS)
 
 Examples : ADC081S101, ADC124S501, ...

